{"tid":552760,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"因航班取消，巴塞球員未能出席尼馬生日派對","createTime":"2018-02-06T23:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T01:22:48.000Z","uid":30040,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"54bc2af5f765231373d8b83aae1c9efa73f768ee","tid":552760,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T23:31:10.000Z","msg":"尼馬在巴黎連開三個派對，慶祝自己的26歲生日，但是沒有一位巴塞球員到場。這是為什麼呢？<br />\n<br />\n哥倫比亞歌手Maluma為尼馬獻唱生日快樂歌<br />\n《每日體育報》消息稱，尼馬邀請了一些關係要好的前巴塞隊友，但是派對時間與巴塞和西班牙人的比賽衝突。而在當地時間本週二，部分巴塞球員受到尼馬邀請來參加第三場派對，也是最私人的一場。與尼馬要好的巴塞球員們準備去參加，但是天公不作美，航班因為天氣原因在最後時刻被取消了，即2月5號下午2點30分飛往巴黎的航班。"},{"pid":"dbd5e84ba90acea0db4fb87db10be151495b3fff","tid":552760,"uid":106701,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T23:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/075736_7acdb17fbec7382bd9a93c1f28c944f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F075736_7acdb17fbec7382bd9a93c1f28c944f2.gif&h=2313b4e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74785a75e1bc6d33b3c7373088668e9c313df31d","tid":552760,"uid":84772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbd5e84ba90acea0db4fb87db10be151495b3fff","tid":552760,"uid":106701,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T23:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/07/075736_7acdb17fbec7382bd9a93c1f28c944f2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F07%2F075736_7acdb17fbec7382bd9a93c1f28c944f2.gif&h=2313b4e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T00:04:11.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑咗出嚟"},{"pid":"d9701d57df55ff04a0b823bdae4639548f01d5f6","tid":552760,"uid":23829,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T00:11:24.000Z","msg":"因航又出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},